# Meme-Aware Response Template

## Purpose
Generate responses that use memes and humor strategically to enhance understanding, retention, and engagement while maintaining technical accuracy.

## Template Variables

| Variable | Type | Required | Description |
|----------|------|----------|-------------|
| content | string | Yes | Technical content to meme-ify |
| meme_level | enum | No | savage/warm/professional (default: warm) |
| target_audience | string | No | Audience for calibration |
| technical_depth | integer | No | 1-10 depth level (default: 5) |
| meme_categories | list | No | Categories of memes to use |

