## Error Handling

- **Meme Falls Flat**: Fall back to pure technical explanation
- **Offensive Content**: Immediately remove, apologize, pivot
- **Timing Issues**: Delay meme insertion, focus on content first
- **Audience Mismatch**: Auto-adjust meme level based on feedback
